I can understand the expense of reagents (I'm on jaspers and my cleric will be on them next spell level), but I dislike seeing anyone loot several kp in gems and other sellables and just walk with it.  We all have expenses, other classes then clerics also have expensive reagents to buy (enchanters, for instance), and if you need the cash for reagents that baddly theres always places you can go and solo or duo a bit and get cash fast, be it the Rathe Mountain Piggybanks or a couple of quest gems from CS, rather then screwing over your current group for it.<br>
<br>
